long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Start a fun adventure game with a super jumping stickman character. Avoid obstacles and reach the highest score. Stick Jump is a fun platform game with 2D graphics. In this game, inspired by popular games such as Doodle Jump, you try to get the highest score by rising between the bars. With your Stickman character, you must be careful while jumping on the sticks and moving forward without hitting the obstacles.

The game's main objective is quite simple: to get the highest score. Your stickman character will automatically move upwards, and your task is to make him jump on the sticks at the right time and reach the highest level. However, there is an important detail that you should pay attention to: there are obstacles between the bars. If you hit the obstacles, you will lose the game.

The graphics and design of the game stand out with the simplicity and elegance of the 2D style. Your Stickman character and sticks are colorful and eye-catching, which makes the game a visually pleasing experience. Fun sound effects make the gameplay even more lively.

Stick Jump is an ideal option for casual and fast-action gamers. Thanks to the simple controls of the game, players of all ages can easily play. However, as you progress, the difficulty level of the game increases, which adds more challenge to the game while also increasing the gameplay.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Stick Jump Stickman Game Features
✓ Infinity Level
✓ Basic control
✓ Realistic Animation
✓ Little Particle

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Stick Jump Stickman Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
